io.delta.kernel.expressions

Class Column

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.delta.kernel.expressions.LeafExpression
      • io.delta.kernel.expressions.Column
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Expression

    public final class Column
extends LeafExpression
    A column whose row-value will be computed based on the data in a Row.

    It is recommended that you instantiate using an existing table schema StructType with StructType.column(int).

    Only supports primitive data types, see Delta Transaction Log Protocol: Primitive Types.
